{"tid":1534551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[碌左兩日twitter］外國無人知狗殺人滅聲呀","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:16.000Z","uid":308041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b22f509d89a3979336037c10171a73fef013dbb1","tid":1534551,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"睇左兩日Twitter d post 全部都係講緊發生左太古恐襲<br />\n但係無人講太古恐襲之後嘅死傷者情況！！<br />\n<br />\n831恐襲記者比狗擋住唔比影<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係打壓新聞自由呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無人放大傷者完全失蹤 生死未卜</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">太子站嘅設施明明無乜損壞<br />\n但係封左勁耐</span><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵又死都唔交cctv出黎<br />\n班狗好可能殺左人<br />\n正喺度毀屍滅跡<br />\n<br />\n依家又突然話有幾個人無啦啦死左<br />\n死因好可疑<br />\n班狗又轉死性極速查案<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲疑點通通都要放大po上Twitter </span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能有人會話件事未有人出黎澄清<br />\n驚會炒車<br />\n<br />\n但依家係講緊幾條人命呀 我地成日講一個都不能少<br />\n唔係講 係做呀<br />\n<br />\n況且我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係講死左班狗一定打死左人<br />\n但係呢次事件班狗嘅作風大變<br />\n我地嘅懷疑係絕對合理</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要講五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n試著說中国政府 非法管轄"},{"pid":"eb3d64fe3a65de925ffd7a3c5fd644bec1b7e052","tid":1534551,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixF